  m_text: 'Left Arrow - Move left

    Right Arrow - Move right

    Up Arrow - Look
    up

    Z - Jump (Unless holding Down Arrow)

    X - Attack

    R - Mark Mode


    Up
    Arrow while touching a ladder - Enter climbing state

    While climbing, use
    Up Arrow and Down Arrow to move up and down and Z to exit the state


    While
    climbing, you can''t move sideways unless Mark Mode is on


    Down Arrow +
    Z while on fall-through platform - Fall through the platform'
