  m_text: '

    Already known issues:

    Fall through platform is wonky. Plans
    for redesign are underway.

    Not leaving collision with an enemy allows you
    to continuesly avoid damage.

    Canvas mechanic is not showcased in this prototype.


    Big
    thanks to Tommy for programming most of the project and making the project. Big
    thanks to Jacob as well for the lovely Doan enemy animation.

    Shoutout to
    Mark for moving sideways on ladder idea.'
